sources.title: Comedy, Family | The Little Princess (1939) | Shirley Temple,Richard Greene, Anita Louise
sources.description:
A little girl is left by her father in an exclusive seminary for girls, due to her father having to go to South Africa to fight in the Second Boer War.

Directors: Walter Lang, William A. Seiter 
Writers: Ethel Hill, Walter Ferris
Stars: Shirley Temple, Richard Greene, Anita Louise 
Genre:  Classics,Comedy, Drama, Family
